author: tkormann
msg: - bug fix in CompositeShapePainter (fix the first NullPointerException
for the first document).
- bug fix for the window size. The document's size was computed using
the svg root element's dimension. The bug appears when external
<image> element where used (anothe root svg element was found and the
document's size was updated). Now, the size of the document is the
outermost svg of the original document.

msg: 1) Removed legacy implementation of TileBlock from source (was

author: deweese
msg: 1) Rewritten TileBlock code that shouldn't ever go off in the weeds, is
simpler, faster, and in simple cases can give better results (in complex
cases it isn't as good).
2) Made getOffscreen syncronized in StaticRenderer, this is the first step
in trying to make the Renderer thread safe (needed for progressive
rendering).
